<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/0> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 0 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. GETTING STARTED"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.1. Grammar Review: tenses, modals and semi-modals, gerunds, nouns as captions, conditional clauses, etc. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/10> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 10 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "10. Planning and Giving an Oral Presentation: Planning a presentation: outlining, using visuals, delivering effectively. Speaking: visual data description and commentary (team presentations based on the Global Marine Trends 2030 report). Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/11> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 11 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "11. The Oral Presentation Project: Researching data and planning the presentation delivery and evaluations Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. 2. Structuring your e-mail message. Main points and supporting point. Tips for successful e-mails. Rewriting inappropriate e-mails. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. Innovations: Talking about accidental discoveries and inventions. Describing methods and procedures Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "4. Design: Spin-offs and Specifications Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "5. Ship Handling ( 1& 2): Parts of a ship, places and positions in ships/ words of rank and on-board, etc. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "6. Career building ( I and 2): Writing a job application, writing a cover letter , Maritime and Oceans Professionals Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/7> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 7 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "7. Systems (I &II) : Product recall notice. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/8> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 8 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "8. Procedures (I and II): Overhaul: Instructions and practical demonstration: action and repair procedures. Summarizing skills: phrases and synonyms Speaking: instructions to explain a repair procedure. How-to speech. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/85003511/2025-26/syllabus/9> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 9 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "9. Reports and Data: Identifying types of visual data: bar charts, flow charts, etc. Interpreting visual data and relating them to relevant sources. Case study: The Global Marine Trends 2030 report. (reading and discussion) Sin subniveles"@es .

